1
00:00:21,199 --> 00:00:23,078
My passion

2
00:00:23,079 --> 00:00:25,119
is like a fire

3
00:00:25,120 --> 00:00:28,160
burning through the desert

4
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:30,000
Going to do laundry?
Yeah.

5
00:00:30,879 --> 00:00:31,879
I'll head over first.

6
00:00:32,119 --> 00:00:32,679
Zhang Shu!
Off to play soccer?

7
00:00:33,399 --> 00:00:34,119
Oh, right.

8
00:00:34,120 --> 00:00:35,200
What time is it?

9
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:36,519
The Hua Country vs. Oman match

10
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:37,599
should be starting soon, right?

11
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:38,718
Fifteen minutes to go.

12
00:00:38,719 --> 00:00:39,560
Fifteen minutes?

13
00:00:39,561 --> 00:00:40,719
Thanks! I gotta run.

14
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:47,520
Yong!
Lin Wen!

15
00:00:48,479 --> 00:00:49,519
What are you guys doing?

16
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:50,839
The Hua Country match is about to start!

17
00:00:50,840 --> 00:00:52,720
You should've said
something! I totally forgot.

18
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:57,520
Brother Xiao-ming!

19
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,640
Brother Xiao-ming!

20
00:00:58,679 --> 00:00:59,679
Where's Yu Lei?

21
00:01:00,119 --> 00:01:01,039
He's across the hall.
Let's go check.

22
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:05,640
Yu Lei!

23
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:07,120
Yu Lei!

24
00:01:07,959 --> 00:01:08,519
What's up?
Where's Yu Lei?

25
00:01:09,319 --> 00:01:09,959
Right here.

26
00:01:09,960 --> 00:01:12,239
I've got a good feeling
about today's match.

27
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,120
Me too.

28
00:01:14,121 --> 00:01:15,358
If we win today,

29
00:01:15,359 --> 00:01:16,560
we'll have 14 points total.

30
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,000
That means we qualify early!
Yu Lei,

31
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:20,000
the broadcast is starting.
What are you still doing?

32
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,000
Hurry up!

33
00:01:22,079 --> 00:01:23,519
Today's match is huge.

34
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:25,256
Who wants to just listen to the radio?

35
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:25,799
Come on.

36
00:01:26,079 --> 00:01:27,719
Let's go watch it on TV in the duty room.

37
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,360
I already cleared it with the dorm lady.

38
00:01:30,519 --> 00:01:31,718
Let's go, everyone!

39
00:01:31,719 --> 00:01:32,400
Let's go!
Move it, move it!

40
00:01:33,079 --> 00:01:34,079
Time for the game!

41
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,640
Hurry up!

42
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,640
Go, go, go!

43
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,120
Wait for me!

44
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,480
Thanks, ma'am!

45
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,000
Here.

46
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:49,040
Come on, come on.

47
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,679
Give me one.

48
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,680
Me too!

49
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,280
And me!

50
00:01:57,079 --> 00:01:57,719
Ready?

51
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,000
Team Hua!
Let's go!

52
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:00,920
Team Hua!
Let's go!

53
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:02,840
Team Hua!
Let's go!

54
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:04,359
It's starting!
Hurry, hurry!

55
00:02:05,121 --> 00:02:07,159
The Hua national
team, with a fresh look...

56
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:08,599
Who's that?

57
00:02:13,919 --> 00:02:15,438
The head referee from Singapore.

58
00:02:15,439 --> 00:02:18,318
And there's the final whistle!

59
00:02:18,319 --> 00:02:20,758
Hua country wins at home, 1-0,

60
00:02:20,759 --> 00:02:22,438
defeating Oman!

61
00:02:22,439 --> 00:02:24,400
With this, Hua country has officially qualified!

62
00:02:25,319 --> 00:02:26,240
That's incredible!

63
00:02:26,319 --> 00:02:27,319
We qualified!

64
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:29,159
Hua Country is the best!

65
00:02:43,159 --> 00:02:44,598
Students, please calm down!

66
00:02:44,599 --> 00:02:45,599
Show some restraint!

67
00:02:45,719 --> 00:02:47,000
Stop smashing your thermoses!

68
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,599
October 2001.

69
00:02:49,919 --> 00:02:51,919
Hua Country made it to the
World Cup for the first time.

70
00:02:52,719 --> 00:02:53,719
They say that night,

71
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:56,160
hundreds of thermoses were
smashed at Ming Univeristy.

72
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:57,800
But for me,

73
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:58,840
the way I celebrated

74
00:02:58,841 --> 00:03:00,359
was heading out into the
rain with my best friends

75
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,480
for a pickup game of soccer.

76
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:04,360
It was on that muddy field

77
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,639
that I met the person

78
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:08,120
who would eventually
define my entire youth.

79
00:03:09,039 --> 00:03:12,080
Have you ever met someone
like that when you were young?

80
00:03:12,919 --> 00:03:14,439
Someone who doesn't have to do a thing

81
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,879
to make you feel completely outmatched?

82
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,159
For me,

83
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:20,560
Chen Ke

84
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,080
was that person.

85
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,120
Come on!

86
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,438
Come on, Chen Ke!

87
00:03:42,439 --> 00:03:43,439
Let's play!

88
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:44,639
Yu Lei,

89
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:45,840
are you crazy?
The ground is still soaked.

90
00:03:46,801 --> 00:03:47,921
You really want to play now?

91
00:03:48,719 --> 00:03:49,199
Come on!

92
00:03:49,599 --> 00:03:50,599
Let's be crazy together!

93
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,439
We met,

94
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:55,639
fell in love,

95
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,120
and truly got to know each other.

96
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,000
But don't get the wrong idea.

97
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,359
Our beginning

98
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,520
wasn't exactly romantic.

99
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,919
Back then, I thought

100
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,598
this guy named Chen Ke

101
00:04:04,599 --> 00:04:05,758
was cold, arrogant,

102
00:04:05,759 --> 00:04:08,960
and clearly destined
to be my rival.

103
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,056
It wasn't until much later that I realized

104
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:13,680
he was the only answer

105
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,319
to all the questions of my youth.

106
00:04:15,500 --> 00:04:21,800
"Feel What You Feel"

107
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:24,800
(Episode 1: Let's Make a Real Bet)

108
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,160
The sky is clear,

109
00:04:27,466 --> 00:04:28,769
the autumn breeze is cool,
and students from all over

110
00:04:28,793 --> 00:04:30,169
(Students today, pillars tomorrow)

111
00:04:32,079 --> 00:04:33,319
are joining our campus

112
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:34,839
to pursue their dreams.

113
00:04:34,864 --> 00:04:36,232
(A new start, the class of
2000, your dream starts here.)

114
00:04:36,256 --> 00:04:39,919
It is an honor to meet you all
at the beautiful Ming University

115
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:43,240
and share in the joy of this new beginning.

116
00:04:46,199 --> 00:04:46,920
Dad!

117
00:04:46,921 --> 00:04:47,959
Hurry up!

118
00:04:51,399 --> 00:04:52,680
You little brat.

119
00:04:58,079 --> 00:05:00,240
August 27, 2000.

120
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,560
Sunny.

121
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,680
This was my first day at Ming University.

122
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,800
And on that same day,

123
00:05:06,519 --> 00:05:08,040
a reckless boy

124
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,680
clumsily crashed into my life.

125
00:05:20,639 --> 00:05:21,360
Hey!

126
00:05:21,361 --> 00:05:22,680
Can you kick the ball back?

127
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,040
Sure.

128
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:25,720
Watch out!

129
00:05:42,759 --> 00:05:43,879
I'm so sorry!

130
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,480
I didn't mean to.

131
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:47,638
Your clothes got dirty.

132
00:05:47,639 --> 00:05:48,800
Let me help you clean it off.

133
00:05:49,079 --> 00:05:50,079
It's fine.

134
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,240
Wait,

135
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:57,199
I'm trying to help and you're annoyed?

136
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,360
Talk about difficult.

137
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,360
You brat.

138
00:06:01,519 --> 00:06:02,679
You're a college student now,

139
00:06:02,759 --> 00:06:03,759
try not to be so clumsy.
Dad,

140
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,839
school hasn't even officially started yet.

141
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,200
Look at that student over there.

142
00:06:08,439 --> 00:06:09,679
He didn't even bring his parents.

143
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:11,120
He's carrying all his own luggage.

144
00:06:11,399 --> 00:06:12,160
Look at you.

145
00:06:12,399 --> 00:06:13,399
Here, take this.

146
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:15,119
Well, you're the one
who insisted on coming.

147
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,120
Let's go.

148
00:06:50,879 --> 00:06:51,680
Who are you?
Hi!

149
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,600
I'm Yu Lei.

150
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,800
I'm in Room 301 too.

151
00:06:56,199 --> 00:06:57,319
So you're Yu Lei?

152
00:06:58,279 --> 00:07:01,999
Does your family own a submarine or
something? Giving you a name like that.

153
00:07:02,024 --> 00:07:03,466
[TN: His name sounds like "torpedo"]

154
00:07:03,759 --> 00:07:04,399
I'm Li Ming.
I'm a sprinter.

155
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:05,959
From now on,

156
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:07,096
we should look out for each other.

157
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,120
Of course.

158
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:08,800
Alright,

159
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:09,920
you're here.

160
00:07:10,079 --> 00:07:11,198
Looks like the whole room

161
00:07:11,199 --> 00:07:12,199
is finally here.

162
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:12,800
Come on.

163
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,319
I'll show you your bunk.

164
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,079
Okay.
Thanks.

165
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:23,920
Hi.

166
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,274
I'm He Jin.
(#1, Chen Ke,
Economic Law, Class A)

167
00:07:26,027 --> 00:07:27,079
We're roommates now.

168
00:07:27,319 --> 00:07:28,319
I'm Chen Ke.

169
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:33,920
I think this is my bunk.

170
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,680
Oh, sorry.

171
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,000
I must have misread it.

172
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,199
Actually,

173
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:40,000
I've always slept by the window.

174
00:07:40,279 --> 00:07:41,480
Do you mind if we switch?

175
00:07:43,399 --> 00:07:44,719
I don't think that's a good idea.

176
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,320
The school already assigned them.

177
00:07:47,279 --> 00:07:48,560
Oh, okay. Sorry about that.

178
00:08:12,839 --> 00:08:13,839
By the way,

179
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:14,759
it's already lunchtime.

180
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:16,119
Why don't we

181
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,279
all go grab a bite?

182
00:08:18,079 --> 00:08:19,079
Sure.

183
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:26,959
I didn't expect that only the
two of us to show up today.

184
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,600
The other two

185
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,720
might be locals.

186
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,800
They probably won't arrive until later.

187
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:36,279
Probably.

188
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:39,799
Hey,

189
00:08:39,800 --> 00:08:40,960
you should try some of mine.

190
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:43,320
This braised pork is really good.

191
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:44,879
No thanks.

192
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:46,079
Braised pork is too greasy for me.

193
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,080
I'm not used to it.

194
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:52,279
There's a made-to-order stall over there.

195
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:53,639
Check the menu.

196
00:08:53,906 --> 00:08:54,906
Maybe

197
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,600
we can go get a side of greens.

198
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,600
Don't bother.

199
00:08:58,679 --> 00:08:59,679
But thanks.

200
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,320
Alright.

201
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,320
So, do you

202
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,639
play soccer?

203
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,600
Yeah.

204
00:09:08,279 --> 00:09:09,639
If you're free this afternoon,

205
00:09:10,159 --> 00:09:11,440
let's go kick the ball around.

206
00:09:13,639 --> 00:09:14,639
Okay.

207
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,599
Come on, come on!

208
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,480
Let's drink!
Cheers!

209
00:09:26,159 --> 00:09:27,159
Cheers!

210
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,158
Not bad, man.

211
00:09:33,159 --> 00:09:34,159
Impressive.

212
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,320
Look,
here's the deal.

213
00:09:38,201 --> 00:09:39,961
I've been here training
for a month already.

214
00:09:40,039 --> 00:09:41,719
If you have any questions about the school,

215
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:42,720
just ask me.
Alright.

216
00:09:43,759 --> 00:09:44,679
I heard

217
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:45,798
the public showers on campus

218
00:09:45,799 --> 00:09:46,799
don't have any stalls.

219
00:09:47,679 --> 00:09:48,679
Is that true?

220
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:53,120
It's true.

221
00:09:53,121 --> 00:09:54,678
Then everyone's just... exposed?

222
00:09:54,679 --> 00:09:55,679
It's a shower.

223
00:09:55,759 --> 00:09:57,158
Everyone's naked anyway.

224
00:09:57,159 --> 00:09:58,279
What's there to see?

225
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:02,399
That's not the point.

226
00:10:03,279 --> 00:10:05,000
Now, if it were girls naked,

227
00:10:05,279 --> 00:10:06,519
that would be something to see.

228
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:12,279
Brother,

229
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:14,558
you clearly haven't experienced

230
00:10:14,559 --> 00:10:16,559
the bathhouse scrub-masters yet.

231
00:10:17,039 --> 00:10:19,119
I highly recommend it.

232
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:21,080
You just lie there on the table,

233
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,558
and the master

234
00:10:22,559 --> 00:10:24,360
scrubs you down like crazy.

235
00:10:24,879 --> 00:10:25,879
It feels amazing.

236
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,480
Wait,

237
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:30,320
how do they scrub you?

238
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,439
Like, your whole body?

239
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,440
Yep.

240
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,679
From head to toe.

241
00:10:35,799 --> 00:10:37,200
Inside and out.

242
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,120
They'll scrub every single nook and cranny

243
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,296
until you're squeaky clean.

244
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,960
Wanna give me a scrub?

245
00:10:42,799 --> 00:10:43,919
Look at you.

246
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:44,559
Come on.
Drink up!

247
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:47,960
Liar.

248
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:54,720
Alright.

249
00:10:54,721 --> 00:10:57,600
Let's head back to the dorm!

250
00:10:58,720 --> 00:10:59,360
Guys,

251
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:01,879
we got everything we need, right?

252
00:11:02,919 --> 00:11:03,919
How about this?

253
00:11:03,920 --> 00:11:05,278
Since I'm free,

254
00:11:05,279 --> 00:11:06,439
let's find an internet cafe

255
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,440
and play some Starcraft.

256
00:11:08,679 --> 00:11:10,360
Maybe another day.

257
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:12,120
I've been unpacking all day.

258
00:11:12,879 --> 00:11:13,799
Right now,

259
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:16,000
I just want to go back and lie down.

260
00:11:16,919 --> 00:11:18,200
What's wrong with you?

261
00:11:19,159 --> 00:11:20,879
You're too young to be this weak.

262
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:22,799
Do you want

263
00:11:22,800 --> 00:11:24,158
me to give you a leg massage

264
00:11:24,159 --> 00:11:25,558
to help you relax?

265
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:26,678
Get away from me,

266
00:11:26,679 --> 00:11:27,440
you creep.

267
00:11:27,441 --> 00:11:28,679
Look at you.

268
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,279
What are you looking at?

269
00:11:51,799 --> 00:11:52,799
A beautiful girl.

270
00:11:53,399 --> 00:11:54,399
A beauty?

271
00:11:54,559 --> 00:11:55,559
You're right.

272
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,279
I'm gonna go get her number.

273
00:11:58,279 --> 00:11:59,319
What are you shouting for?

274
00:11:59,399 --> 00:12:00,399
That's my sister.

275
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:02,840
Your sister?

276
00:12:02,919 --> 00:12:04,080
Your sister?

277
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:08,919
Thanks.

278
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:10,080
No problem.

279
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:11,758
You're Chen Ke, right?

280
00:12:11,759 --> 00:12:13,639
A freshman at the Law School?

281
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:14,919
Yes.

282
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,080
And you are?

283
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:18,159
We met at the registration desk today.

284
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,240
I'm Zhang Han.

285
00:12:19,639 --> 00:12:20,639
Sis!

286
00:12:20,759 --> 00:12:21,759
What are you doing here?

287
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,735
I just went to your dorm
but couldn't find you.

288
00:12:23,759 --> 00:12:25,239
I didn't expect to run into you here.

289
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:26,840
Let's go, Sis.

290
00:12:26,841 --> 00:12:28,240
I have so much to tell you.

291
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:34,398
Sis, you had the whole day.

292
00:12:34,399 --> 00:12:36,120
Why did it take you so long to find me?

293
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:38,080
I was just elected Student Union President.

294
00:12:38,279 --> 00:12:40,279
I've been busy welcoming freshmen all day.

295
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,799
I just finished.

296
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:42,919
So, Lei-lei,

297
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:44,080
is your dorm all set up?

298
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,039
It's fine.

299
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:46,680
I've finished organizing everything.

300
00:12:47,039 --> 00:12:48,278
The school mattresses are thin.

301
00:12:48,279 --> 00:12:49,576
I figured you wouldn't be comfortable,

302
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,960
so I bought you a new one.

303
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:52,558
You weren't in your room,

304
00:12:52,559 --> 00:12:53,918
so I left it with the dorm lady.

305
00:12:53,919 --> 00:12:54,679
Don't forget to pick it up.

306
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:56,000
Okay, thanks Sis.

307
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:58,439
If you need anything else,

308
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,440
just let me know.

309
00:13:00,159 --> 00:13:01,159
I'm all set.

310
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:03,079
Mom and Dad even bought extra stuff

311
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,159
for me to bring to you.

312
00:13:04,799 --> 00:13:05,679
Hello, senior.

313
00:13:05,759 --> 00:13:06,759
Hi.

314
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:09,200
That's good then.

315
00:13:09,399 --> 00:13:10,799
What are you looking at?

316
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:13,375
Are you getting along with your roommates?

317
00:13:13,399 --> 00:13:14,559
Of course.

318
00:13:14,679 --> 00:13:16,599
Your brother is handsome and smart.

319
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,480
Everyone loves me.

320
00:13:17,481 --> 00:13:18,735
Even the flowers bloom when I walk by.

321
00:13:18,759 --> 00:13:20,039
See? They're blooming right now.

322
00:13:21,279 --> 00:13:22,039
Don't worry.

323
00:13:22,040 --> 00:13:23,440
I'll do great anywhere.

324
00:13:24,879 --> 00:13:26,319
This is Ming University.

325
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:28,199
There are talented people everywhere.

326
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:30,879
Don't be so arrogant.

327
00:13:30,919 --> 00:13:32,759
Who's being arrogant?

328
00:13:32,879 --> 00:13:35,080
I was the top scorer in the
city on the entrance exam.

329
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:37,000
Could there really be
someone better than me?

330
00:13:37,559 --> 00:13:38,120
Where?

331
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,440
Where are they?

332
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,559
There you go again.

333
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,840
In your class alone,

334
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,919
there's someone with
better grades than you.

335
00:13:47,399 --> 00:13:48,399
Really?

336
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:49,759
I don't believe it.

337
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:51,279
Why would I lie?

338
00:13:51,327 --> 00:13:52,406
In your class, there's someone named Chen Ke.

339
00:13:52,639 --> 00:13:53,878
His entrance exam score

340
00:13:53,879 --> 00:13:56,399
was the highest in the entire Law School.

341
00:13:56,559 --> 00:13:57,399
There's always someone better.

342
00:13:57,400 --> 00:13:58,599
The world is bigger than you think.

343
00:13:58,600 --> 00:14:00,840
Try to be a little more humble.

344
00:14:01,879 --> 00:14:03,480
So my class has someone like that?

345
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:05,919
I'll have to see it for myself.

346
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,360
You've already met him.

347
00:14:08,039 --> 00:14:09,960
The boy I was just talking to.

348
00:14:11,759 --> 00:14:12,759
Him?

349
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:18,399
Hello, everyone.

350
00:14:23,279 --> 00:14:26,239
Welcome to the Economic Law program.

351
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:27,000
This semester,

352
00:14:27,001 --> 00:14:28,798
each of you

353
00:14:28,799 --> 00:14:30,319
has a blank sheet of paper before you.

354
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,279
Chen
Ke.

355
00:14:32,040 --> 00:14:33,319
If you choose

356
00:14:33,320 --> 00:14:34,919
hard work and perseverance,

357
00:14:35,120 --> 00:14:35,840
then

358
00:14:35,841 --> 00:14:39,120
you will find success and fulfillment.

359
00:14:39,679 --> 00:14:41,079
But if you choose

360
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:43,000
laziness and retreating,

361
00:14:43,279 --> 00:14:43,879
then what awaits you...

362
00:14:43,880 --> 00:14:45,119
Height...

363
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:46,000
will still be a blank sheet of paper.
About 180 cm.

364
00:14:47,639 --> 00:14:48,279
Not as tall as me.
A good start

365
00:14:49,040 --> 00:14:50,119
is the beginning of success.

366
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:51,559
Entrance exam score...

367
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:53,398
You are at a point in your lives...

368
00:14:53,399 --> 00:14:55,200
A bit better than me.

369
00:14:55,279 --> 00:14:56,558
You can all become a
new version of yourselves.

370
00:14:56,559 --> 00:14:57,480
Who are you drawing?

371
00:14:57,481 --> 00:14:59,159
Does everyone believe in themselvves?

372
00:14:59,399 --> 00:15:00,200
Yes!

373
00:15:00,201 --> 00:15:01,799
Give yourselves a round of applause.

374
00:15:05,919 --> 00:15:06,840
Alright, students.
Next,

375
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:10,239
let's have another warm welcome.

376
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:11,758
Chen Ke,

377
00:15:11,759 --> 00:15:13,679
please come up and introduce yourself.

378
00:15:19,759 --> 00:15:21,479
Hi everyone, I'm Chen Ke.

379
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:23,360
C-H-E-N K-E.

380
00:15:23,879 --> 00:15:24,919
I live by the sea.

381
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,399
I build model ships,

382
00:15:26,559 --> 00:15:27,959
read manga,

383
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:28,960
and play soccer.

384
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:31,200
Nothing special about him.

385
00:15:31,279 --> 00:15:32,559
Just a bookworm.

386
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:38,278
And now,

387
00:15:38,279 --> 00:15:40,479
let's welcome Yu Lei

388
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:41,759
to introduce himself.

389
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:47,439
Hi everyone.

390
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:48,399
I'm Yu Lei.

391
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:50,079
It's not 'Torpedo' like the weapon.

392
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:51,319
It's 'Yu' as in 'equal to'

393
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:52,440
and 'Lei' as in 'thunder'.

394
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:54,398
I love sports,

395
00:15:54,399 --> 00:15:56,080
gaming, and anime.

396
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:58,840
If anyone wants to play CS

397
00:15:59,039 --> 00:16:00,679
or needs someone for soccer,

398
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:02,080
just let me know.

399
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:04,039
Thanks.

400
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:13,158
Youth should look like youth.

401
00:16:13,159 --> 00:16:15,879
We should let our
youth bloom to the fullest.

402
00:16:19,039 --> 00:16:20,960
Students, time is short.

403
00:16:21,080 --> 00:16:22,159
Next,

404
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:24,278
we need to choose a student

405
00:16:24,279 --> 00:16:25,840
from our class

406
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:27,878
to be in charge of

407
00:16:27,879 --> 00:16:29,119
class affairs this semester.

408
00:16:29,120 --> 00:16:31,120
Does anyone want to volunteer?

409
00:16:31,279 --> 00:16:32,639
Professor, how about me?

410
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:35,919
Yu Lei.

411
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:39,199
Does everyone think
Yu Lei is up for the task?

412
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:40,599
Yes!

413
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:41,600
Good.

414
00:16:43,279 --> 00:16:44,599
Then for this semester,

415
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:45,719
Yu Lei

416
00:16:45,720 --> 00:16:47,279
will be our class monitor.

417
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:48,678
I hope Yu Lei

418
00:16:48,679 --> 00:16:49,600
will work hard

419
00:16:49,601 --> 00:16:50,839
and contribute

420
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:51,840
to our class community.

421
00:16:52,159 --> 00:16:53,439
Let's give another round of applause

422
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:54,839
to Yu Lei.

423
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:55,600
No problem.

424
00:16:55,601 --> 00:16:57,639
Let's give him another hand.

425
00:17:08,359 --> 00:17:09,359
Yu Lei,

426
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:11,280
are you sure you don't
want to shower with us?

427
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:13,160
No thanks.

428
00:17:13,480 --> 00:17:14,639
You guys go ahead.

429
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:15,960
I'll just wash up here.

430
00:17:17,119 --> 00:17:18,079
Alright, we're heading out.
Okay.

431
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:25,680
What's the deal with Chen Ke?

432
00:17:26,279 --> 00:17:28,160
Why is my sister so interested in him?

433
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:36,758
Love is love,

434
00:17:36,759 --> 00:17:40,279
no need to be generous with feelings.

435
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:44,318
No one needs to give me a golden age,

436
00:17:44,319 --> 00:17:47,400
I want you right now.

437
00:17:53,160 --> 00:17:55,240
I'm clearly the most handsome
and talented one here.

438
00:18:10,359 --> 00:18:12,279
Hey, your washbasin!

439
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:33,759
Wasn't that Chen Ke just now?

440
00:18:37,279 --> 00:18:38,279
What bad luck.

441
00:18:44,279 --> 00:18:45,640
This is so annoying.

442
00:18:45,752 --> 00:18:48,352
My sister actually thinks
Chen Ke is better than me.

443
00:18:48,799 --> 00:18:49,440
Who even is Chen Ke?

444
00:18:49,441 --> 00:18:50,640
Who is he?

445
00:18:53,240 --> 00:18:55,440
Just a guy acting all deep.

446
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:57,599
What's so great about him?

447
00:18:59,039 --> 00:19:01,199
He had that sour face on registration day.

448
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,200
So unapproachable.

449
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:05,400
And yet my sister remembered his name.

450
00:19:07,680 --> 00:19:10,039
His introduction in class was so dry too.

451
00:19:10,279 --> 00:19:11,279
Total bookworm.

452
00:19:13,200 --> 00:19:15,240
He ignores his roommates too.

453
00:19:15,480 --> 00:19:16,720
Clearly, he's not very popular.

454
00:19:17,640 --> 00:19:19,599
I'm definitely the coolest one.

455
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:21,160
Yeah!

456
00:19:26,440 --> 00:19:28,559
Brother Xiao-ming, when did you get back?

457
00:19:28,759 --> 00:19:30,719
I've been standing here
watching you for a while.

458
00:19:31,160 --> 00:19:33,440
Just watching you grin
while chatting with girls.

459
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:44,079
I'm the one who backed
you for class monitor!

460
00:19:44,279 --> 00:19:45,279
Is this how you repay me?

461
00:19:45,319 --> 00:19:47,200
You won't introduce
me to your pretty cousin,

462
00:19:47,279 --> 00:19:48,999
and now you're sneaking around

463
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:50,240
chatting with girls online.

464
00:19:50,359 --> 00:19:52,399
Keeping them all to yourself
is shameful, you know?

465
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:53,759
Brother Xiao-ming,

466
00:19:53,799 --> 00:19:54,480
you've got it all wrong!
Let me explain.

467
00:19:55,079 --> 00:19:56,079
Explain?

468
00:19:56,160 --> 00:19:57,119
Explaining is just covering it up.

469
00:19:57,120 --> 00:19:58,735
And covering it up
means it's definitely true.

470
00:19:58,759 --> 00:19:59,279
Save it.

471
00:19:59,480 --> 00:20:01,800
I sentence you to death by
hanging, effective immediately.

472
00:20:02,440 --> 00:20:03,920
Brother Xiao-ming, Brother Xiao-ming!

473
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:05,199
I've got things to do.

474
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:06,880
I'll introduce you next time, okay?

475
00:20:08,759 --> 00:20:10,119
You better not be messing with me.

476
00:20:11,915 --> 00:20:15,135
Ming De University Club New Recruiting Area

477
00:20:15,160 --> 00:20:16,319
Hey, come join us!

478
00:20:16,559 --> 00:20:17,160
Come take a look!

479
00:20:17,161 --> 00:20:18,599
Street Dance Club recruitment!

480
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:20,078
Check it out, everyone!

481
00:20:20,079 --> 00:20:21,399
Street Dance Club welcoming new members!

482
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:22,400
Come on, come on!

483
00:20:22,720 --> 00:20:23,959
Join the Street Dance Club!

484
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:25,680
Anyone want to learn how to street dance?

485
00:20:26,359 --> 00:20:27,240
Learn about our Baseball Club!
Everyone!

486
00:20:27,921 --> 00:20:29,079
Come on, come on!

487
00:20:30,119 --> 00:20:31,759
Hey beautiful, want to learn street dance?

488
00:20:32,839 --> 00:20:34,119
Ladies, come learn street dance!

489
00:20:35,119 --> 00:20:36,439
Take a look, everyone!

490
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:37,640
Street Dance Club recruitment!

491
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:42,880
Hey, Thunder.

492
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:08,279
o o?

493
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:10,480
Wait, you're a guy?

494
00:21:11,799 --> 00:21:13,400
I never said I was a girl.

495
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:15,200
I just thought

496
00:21:18,559 --> 00:21:20,879
great souls were always androgynous.

497
00:21:20,880 --> 00:21:22,240
If that's how you see me,

498
00:21:22,279 --> 00:21:25,000
I'll take it as a
compliment to my soul.

499
00:21:26,319 --> 00:21:27,440
So,

500
00:21:28,119 --> 00:21:29,559
does that mean you've fallen for me?

501
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:30,839
Me?
Don't talk nonsense.

502
00:21:31,759 --> 00:21:32,759
I have not.

503
00:21:34,376 --> 00:21:36,734
Since our souls resonated online,

504
00:21:36,759 --> 00:21:37,759
I'm sure

505
00:21:37,760 --> 00:21:39,480
we'll have some chemistry in real life too.

506
00:21:39,799 --> 00:21:41,839
Thunder, I'm fine with it.

507
00:21:42,319 --> 00:21:43,400
Stop making excuses.

508
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:44,559
I'm not!

509
00:21:44,560 --> 00:21:46,079
Don't go ruining my reputation.

510
00:21:46,319 --> 00:21:47,240
Besides,

511
00:21:47,241 --> 00:21:48,358
opposites attract,

512
00:21:48,359 --> 00:21:49,440
like poles repel.

513
00:21:49,480 --> 00:21:51,080
Did you even pass middle school physics?

514
00:21:53,319 --> 00:21:54,440
Drama Club!

515
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:56,839
Comedy Club!

516
00:21:56,840 --> 00:21:58,359
Check out the Comedy Club!

517
00:22:00,480 --> 00:22:02,119
We even have a Baseball Club.

518
00:22:02,160 --> 00:22:03,160
That's pretty trendy.

519
00:22:04,839 --> 00:22:06,000
What is he doing here?

520
00:22:06,079 --> 00:22:07,079
Who?

521
00:22:07,319 --> 00:22:08,960
That annoying guy, Chen Ke.

522
00:22:10,319 --> 00:22:11,319
What a buzzkill.

523
00:22:14,680 --> 00:22:16,838
Yu Lei, what a coincidence.

524
00:22:16,839 --> 00:22:18,239
Yeah, just checking things out.

525
00:22:18,240 --> 00:22:20,359
Are you interested in baseball too?

526
00:22:21,240 --> 00:22:22,279
It's alright.

527
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:25,480
Lei-lei,

528
00:22:25,759 --> 00:22:27,920
how come you didn't tell me
you became class monitor?

529
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:28,640
Sis,

530
00:22:28,640 --> 00:22:31,079
I was just about to go find
you at the Student Union booth.

531
00:22:31,119 --> 00:22:32,240
I wanted to surprise you.

532
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:33,599
Alright.

533
00:22:35,079 --> 00:22:35,920
Chen Ke,

534
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:37,079
I was looking for you.

535
00:22:37,480 --> 00:22:38,599
Senior.

536
00:22:38,839 --> 00:22:40,960
The school is hosting a freshman gala.

537
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:42,920
I know you're a Level 10 pianist.

538
00:22:43,279 --> 00:22:44,358
Would you be interested

539
00:22:44,359 --> 00:22:45,679
in representing the Law School

540
00:22:45,680 --> 00:22:46,680
with a performance?

541
00:22:49,039 --> 00:22:50,200
Are you jealous?

542
00:22:50,599 --> 00:22:52,359
And you say you don't
have a sister complex.

543
00:22:53,039 --> 00:22:54,039
Shut up.

544
00:22:54,319 --> 00:22:55,440
It's not like that.

545
00:22:56,559 --> 00:22:58,200
Sure, I'll do it.

546
00:22:58,359 --> 00:22:59,160
Great!

547
00:22:59,161 --> 00:23:00,839
I'll go get the application form for you.

548
00:23:17,279 --> 00:23:18,720
You can even skip stones?

549
00:23:21,160 --> 00:23:22,160
Tell me,

550
00:23:24,440 --> 00:23:25,680
is playing the piano

551
00:23:25,880 --> 00:23:27,079
really that impressive?

552
00:23:30,119 --> 00:23:31,720
Playing at level 10?

553
00:23:32,359 --> 00:23:33,879
Yeah, that's actually very impressive.

554
00:23:37,559 --> 00:23:38,559
But

555
00:23:39,039 --> 00:23:40,799
I became class monitor,
which is a big deal,

556
00:23:40,880 --> 00:23:42,040
and she barely said anything.

557
00:23:42,680 --> 00:23:44,720
Then she turns around and
only cares about Chen Ke.

558
00:23:47,599 --> 00:23:49,798
Must be that chemistry I mentioned.

559
00:23:49,799 --> 00:23:50,799
You...

560
00:23:51,279 --> 00:23:53,720
To prepare for the 2000 Asian Cup,

561
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:57,078
the Hua men's soccer
team plans to play several

562
00:23:57,079 --> 00:23:58,119
friendly warm-up matches.

563
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:00,400
That's it!

564
00:24:00,759 --> 00:24:02,680
I'm definitely going to get even.

565
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:07,960
Guys!

566
00:24:07,961 --> 00:24:10,480
Room 301 actually sent us a challenge!

567
00:24:12,799 --> 00:24:15,359
To celebrate the 2000 Asian Cup,

568
00:24:15,480 --> 00:24:18,038
Room 301 invites Room 312

569
00:24:18,039 --> 00:24:20,039
to a 4-on-4 friendly soccer match.

570
00:24:20,319 --> 00:24:22,239
Friendship first, competition second.

571
00:24:22,240 --> 00:24:24,480
Losers buy the Cokes.

572
00:24:25,039 --> 00:24:26,079
This is so sudden.

573
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:27,400
And surprisingly formal.

574
00:24:27,615 --> 00:24:28,615
I have no idea either.

575
00:24:28,640 --> 00:24:29,400
As soon as I got back,

576
00:24:29,401 --> 00:24:31,319
Yu Lei from 301 handed me this challenge.

577
00:24:31,720 --> 00:24:32,440
So, guys,

578
00:24:32,441 --> 00:24:33,799
should we accept?

579
00:24:33,960 --> 00:24:34,759
We're already here.
Why not?

580
00:24:35,920 --> 00:24:37,000
What do you think, Chen Ke?

581
00:24:37,720 --> 00:24:39,199
It's just a friendly match.

582
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,200
Let's play.

583
00:24:40,640 --> 00:24:42,039
Alright, let's do it.

584
00:24:42,240 --> 00:24:44,319
Let's show them what Room 312 is made of.

585
00:24:44,720 --> 00:24:46,239
We'll crush them!

586
00:24:46,240 --> 00:24:47,839
Yeah, crush them!

587
00:24:47,960 --> 00:24:49,278
Come on, guys!

588
00:24:49,279 --> 00:24:50,318
312

589
00:24:50,319 --> 00:24:51,319
Victory!

590
00:24:54,319 --> 00:24:55,240
President,

591
00:24:55,241 --> 00:24:57,318
I've decided on my piece for the gala.

592
00:24:57,319 --> 00:24:58,319
Here's the form.

593
00:24:59,039 --> 00:25:00,279
Moonlight Sonata.

594
00:25:00,720 --> 00:25:01,760
I'm looking forward to it.

595
00:25:02,079 --> 00:25:03,200
Thank you, President.

596
00:25:03,359 --> 00:25:04,439
Stop calling me President.

597
00:25:04,440 --> 00:25:05,640
It sounds so weird.

598
00:25:05,799 --> 00:25:06,799
Just use my name,

599
00:25:07,079 --> 00:25:08,759
or call me 'Senior'.

600
00:25:09,640 --> 00:25:10,240
Okay.

601
00:25:10,599 --> 00:25:11,720
Thanks, Senior.

602
00:25:18,319 --> 00:25:18,960
Sis!

603
00:25:18,961 --> 00:25:20,559
I want to sign up for the gala too.

604
00:25:20,799 --> 00:25:22,159
Show some respect.

605
00:25:22,160 --> 00:25:23,400
Call me President.

606
00:25:23,680 --> 00:25:24,640
Fine.

607
00:25:24,641 --> 00:25:26,039
President Zhang.

608
00:25:27,279 --> 00:25:28,399
Didn't you say

609
00:25:28,400 --> 00:25:30,358
you were sick of hosting galas

610
00:25:30,359 --> 00:25:31,735
after doing it for three
years in high school?

611
00:25:31,759 --> 00:25:33,279
That was then.

612
00:25:33,440 --> 00:25:34,440
Besides,
college

613
00:25:35,559 --> 00:25:37,039
is different from high school.

614
00:25:37,279 --> 00:25:39,119
I need to make a grand entrance.

615
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:42,119
Tone it down a bit.

616
00:25:42,799 --> 00:25:44,439
Auditions are next week.

617
00:25:44,440 --> 00:25:46,000
You two better be prepared.

618
00:25:46,880 --> 00:25:47,680
Okay.

619
00:25:47,799 --> 00:25:48,799
Yes, ma'am!

620
00:25:49,559 --> 00:25:50,559
By the way, Chen Ke,

621
00:25:50,880 --> 00:25:52,278
about the match this afternoon,

622
00:25:52,279 --> 00:25:54,400
don't let Room 312 chicken out.

623
00:25:55,079 --> 00:25:56,079
We won't.

624
00:25:56,400 --> 00:25:57,760
You guys are playing soccer today?

625
00:25:58,319 --> 00:25:59,160
Yeah, Sis.

626
00:25:59,240 --> 00:26:01,400
Room 301 challenged
them to a friendly match.

627
00:26:02,160 --> 00:26:04,200
You should come watch!

628
00:26:04,296 --> 00:26:05,318
I'm busy this afternoon

629
00:26:05,319 --> 00:26:07,200
with Student Union gala prep.

630
00:26:07,279 --> 00:26:08,160
I can't make it.

631
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:09,240
Oh, okay.

632
00:26:10,119 --> 00:26:12,160
Lei-lei, take it easy out there.

633
00:26:12,279 --> 00:26:13,696
Don't go getting injured
right at the start of the term.

634
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:14,720
I know.

635
00:26:14,799 --> 00:26:15,480
Chen Ke,

636
00:26:15,505 --> 00:26:17,303
go easy on our Yu Lei, okay?

637
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:20,200
No problem.

638
00:26:20,440 --> 00:26:21,319
Sis!

639
00:26:21,373 --> 00:26:23,532
I don't need him to go easy on me.

640
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:45,160
Didn't you say your sister

641
00:26:45,161 --> 00:26:46,278
was coming to watch us play?

642
00:26:46,279 --> 00:26:46,839
Where is she?

643
00:26:47,279 --> 00:26:48,359
I asked her!

644
00:26:48,599 --> 00:26:49,599
I really did.

645
00:26:49,600 --> 00:26:51,359
She's just too busy with the Student Union.

646
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:52,440
Well,

647
00:26:52,480 --> 00:26:53,279
look over there.
See?

648
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:54,359
There are

649
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:55,880
plenty of other spectators.

650
00:26:56,119 --> 00:26:56,960
Take a good look.

651
00:26:56,961 --> 00:26:58,321
What kind of spectators are those?

652
00:27:02,799 --> 00:27:03,839
Go Yu Lei!

653
00:27:06,599 --> 00:27:07,640
Li Ming!

654
00:27:12,720 --> 00:27:14,839
Legs feeling weak without any girls around?

655
00:27:15,759 --> 00:27:16,960
Shut it, Liu Haibin!

656
00:27:17,319 --> 00:27:18,440
Even on my worst day,

657
00:27:18,599 --> 00:27:20,359
I can still outrun a shot-putter like you.

658
00:27:20,720 --> 00:27:21,838
Right, guys?

659
00:27:21,839 --> 00:27:22,920
Right!

660
00:27:26,599 --> 00:27:28,000
What's the use of being fast?

661
00:27:28,480 --> 00:27:29,799
You actually have to score!

662
00:27:30,279 --> 00:27:31,358
My roommates

663
00:27:31,359 --> 00:27:32,558
aren't exactly pushovers.

664
00:27:32,559 --> 00:27:33,759
Well, sorry to say,

665
00:27:34,000 --> 00:27:34,720
but today,

666
00:27:34,721 --> 00:27:36,799
you're going home with a big fat zero.

667
00:28:09,119 --> 00:28:10,119
Go!

668
00:28:12,799 --> 00:28:13,960
Get the ball!

669
00:28:14,799 --> 00:28:15,480
Break through the middle!
Pass it! Pass it!

670
00:28:19,359 --> 00:28:20,359
Run!

671
00:28:41,160 --> 00:28:42,160
Here, have some water.

672
00:28:48,279 --> 00:28:49,440
He's barely even sweating.

673
00:28:49,759 --> 00:28:50,839
Is he looking down on me?

674
00:28:51,839 --> 00:28:53,160
Next half, we'll play man-to-man.

675
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:54,240
You go mark him.

676
00:28:54,359 --> 00:28:55,960
Maybe.

677
00:28:57,440 --> 00:28:59,359
Lei-lei, take it easy out there.

678
00:28:59,599 --> 00:29:00,879
Don't go getting injured
right at the start of the term.

679
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:01,880
I know.

680
00:29:02,119 --> 00:29:02,759
Chen Ke,

681
00:29:02,760 --> 00:29:04,640
go easy on our Yu Lei, okay?

682
00:29:05,079 --> 00:29:06,079
No problem.

683
00:29:12,119 --> 00:29:12,960
Sorry,

684
00:29:12,961 --> 00:29:14,521
I need to talk to Chen Ke for a second.

685
00:29:15,559 --> 00:29:16,559
What's going on?

686
00:29:16,759 --> 00:29:17,759
No idea.

687
00:29:19,799 --> 00:29:21,440
Can you take this game seriously?

688
00:29:21,880 --> 00:29:23,359
I am taking it seriously.

689
00:29:23,440 --> 00:29:25,119
Besides, it's just a friendly match.

690
00:29:27,119 --> 00:29:27,759
Do you think

691
00:29:27,760 --> 00:29:28,920
betting just Cokes is boring?

692
00:29:29,160 --> 00:29:30,240
Then let's make a real bet.

693
00:29:30,440 --> 00:29:31,119
Whoever loses

694
00:29:31,120 --> 00:29:32,839
can't talk to Zhang Han for a month.

695
00:29:56,400 --> 00:29:57,558
Chen Ke is so cool!

696
00:29:57,559 --> 00:29:59,278
Chen Ke is amazing!

697
00:29:59,279 --> 00:30:00,480
What a goal!

698
00:30:00,839 --> 00:30:02,000
It's 1-0!

699
00:30:03,279 --> 00:30:04,279
What's the rush?

700
00:30:04,559 --> 00:30:06,119
The ball is round, anything can happen.

701
00:30:06,480 --> 00:30:07,039
Give it a rest.

702
00:30:07,319 --> 00:30:09,079
Just get ready to buy us those Cokes.

703
00:30:09,319 --> 00:30:10,359
You just wait.

704
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:37,960
Did you do that on purpose?

705
00:30:38,160 --> 00:30:38,759
Brother Xiao-ming, Brother Xiao-ming!
Play the ball, not the man!

706
00:30:39,319 --> 00:30:40,160
Don't do anything stupid!
Calm down, calm down!

707
00:30:40,880 --> 00:30:41,440
Don't lose your head!

708
00:30:41,441 --> 00:30:42,799
I didn't mean it! Calm down!

709
00:30:42,839 --> 00:30:43,400
Yu Lei,
are you okay?

710
00:30:44,359 --> 00:30:45,680
I was just defending normally.

711
00:30:46,279 --> 00:30:47,160
Who knew...

712
00:30:47,279 --> 00:30:48,318
You have some nerve!

713
00:30:48,319 --> 00:30:49,279
Don't do anything stupid!
Wait, wait, wait!

714
00:30:49,721 --> 00:30:51,200
I really didn't mean it.

715
00:30:51,359 --> 00:30:52,400
Stop shouting, everyone!

716
00:30:52,440 --> 00:30:53,000
Let me see
how bad it is.

717
00:30:55,759 --> 00:30:56,959
Do you know what you're doing?

718
00:30:57,319 --> 00:30:58,679
Yeah, I have experience with this.

719
00:30:59,359 --> 00:31:00,680
It's fine, I don't need...

720
00:31:01,400 --> 00:31:02,400
Just leave me alone.

721
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:04,559
It's not too bad.
Nothing's broken.

722
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:06,200
Quick,

723
00:31:06,559 --> 00:31:07,598
I'll take you to the infirmary.

724
00:31:07,599 --> 00:31:08,599
Come on.

725
00:31:09,960 --> 00:31:10,960
Up you go.

726
00:31:13,240 --> 00:31:14,240
Easy now.

727
00:31:17,640 --> 00:31:19,520
If anything happens to
him, I'm coming for you.

728
00:31:21,039 --> 00:31:23,359
September 7, 2000. Sunny.

729
00:31:24,480 --> 00:31:25,240
That day's match

730
00:31:25,241 --> 00:31:26,798
ended in total chaos.

731
00:31:26,799 --> 00:31:27,599
Don't take it to heart.

732
00:31:27,759 --> 00:31:28,759
I heard

733
00:31:29,079 --> 00:31:30,999
He Jin stayed on the field
by himself for a long time.

734
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:32,118
It's okay, it really wasn't your fault.

735
00:31:32,119 --> 00:31:33,879
He didn't say another
word to us that night.

736
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:37,799
Even though Yu Lei's challenge was strange,

737
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:39,400
at least

738
00:31:39,720 --> 00:31:40,760
his injury wasn't serious.

739
00:32:00,519 --> 00:32:02,359
Alright, Master Yu,

740
00:32:02,640 --> 00:32:04,279
that's enough.

741
00:32:04,480 --> 00:32:05,879
You've used half a bottle

742
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:07,759
of medicated oil in one go.

743
00:32:07,960 --> 00:32:08,640
People will think

744
00:32:08,641 --> 00:32:10,440
you're trying to deep-fry chicken wings.

745
00:32:12,799 --> 00:32:14,400
Have some sympathy, will you?

746
00:32:15,079 --> 00:32:16,199
What do you mean, deep-fry chicken wings?

747
00:32:16,200 --> 00:32:17,758
Can't you see my foot is
swollen like a pig's trotter?

748
00:32:17,759 --> 00:32:18,599
I don't know,

749
00:32:18,720 --> 00:32:20,240
it doesn't look swollen to me.

750
00:32:20,519 --> 00:32:22,559
It's been several days.

751
00:32:22,960 --> 00:32:24,416
The swelling must have gone down by now.

752
00:32:24,440 --> 00:32:26,720
It's a good thing Chen Ke
carried you to the infirmary.

753
00:32:27,119 --> 00:32:28,639
Who knew he was actually a decent guy?

754
00:32:32,119 --> 00:32:33,639
You guys don't get it.

755
00:32:33,640 --> 00:32:36,039
A bone injury takes a hundred days to heal.

756
00:32:38,160 --> 00:32:39,160
I'm done with you guys.

757
00:32:39,279 --> 00:32:40,279
I'm going.

758
00:32:40,839 --> 00:32:41,839
Going where?

759
00:32:42,279 --> 00:32:43,279
To the bathroom.

760
00:32:43,359 --> 00:32:45,200
We'll go with you.

761
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:47,758
I'm not going to the bathroom!

762
00:32:47,759 --> 00:32:49,278
Then where? I'm going to the library.

763
00:32:49,279 --> 00:32:50,279
Don't be so polite.

764
00:32:50,280 --> 00:32:51,319
You don't need help?

765
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:52,720
I really don't!

766
00:32:53,759 --> 00:32:54,759
Look at him.

767
00:32:55,160 --> 00:32:56,400
What is he up to every day?

768
00:33:25,559 --> 00:33:27,359
What is he doing here?

769
00:33:28,319 --> 00:33:30,119
Should I say something?

770
00:33:31,000 --> 00:33:32,000
Yu Lei.

771
00:33:34,720 --> 00:33:35,759
Is your foot better?

772
00:33:36,000 --> 00:33:37,000
About last time,

773
00:33:37,400 --> 00:33:38,400
I'm really sorry.

774
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:40,160
It's no big deal.

775
00:33:40,440 --> 00:33:40,839
Really.

776
00:33:40,977 --> 00:33:42,520
I didn't even give it a second thought.

777
00:33:42,599 --> 00:33:43,880
Quiet, please.

778
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:45,240
If you want to talk, go outside.

779
00:33:45,279 --> 00:33:45,920
Sorry.

780
00:33:46,119 --> 00:33:47,119
Sorry, Professor.

781
00:33:56,079 --> 00:33:57,440
What's his problem?

782
00:34:33,079 --> 00:34:35,480
September 14, 2000. Sunny.

783
00:34:36,320 --> 00:34:37,320
Today,

784
00:34:37,605 --> 00:34:39,446
looking at the note Yu Lei handed me,

785
00:34:39,471 --> 00:34:40,395
"Sorry for making you go to
the trouble last time on the court!"

786
00:34:40,427 --> 00:34:42,559
it felt a bit nonsensical,
but also kind of cute.

787
00:34:44,400 --> 00:34:45,479
Will we become friends?

788
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:46,679
No worries.

789
00:34:47,159 --> 00:34:48,159
For some reason,

790
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:49,760
I find myself looking forward to it.

791
00:34:50,320 --> 00:34:51,320
Are you okay?

792
00:34:52,039 --> 00:34:53,039
I'm fine.

793
00:35:14,760 --> 00:35:16,480
There's still the freshman gala.

794
00:35:16,960 --> 00:35:18,440
I'm definitely going to win that one.

795
00:35:27,903 --> 00:35:30,856
(Grand Hall)
(Ming De University 2000 Welcoming Gala)

796
00:35:31,599 --> 00:35:33,456
(Next Episode)
Chen Ke's performance was canceled.

797
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:35,518
But why only Chen Ke's?

798
00:35:35,519 --> 00:35:36,559
Why not anyone else's?

799
00:35:37,440 --> 00:35:38,800
Why do you think?

800
00:35:39,639 --> 00:35:40,879
It's rigged!

801
00:35:40,880 --> 00:35:43,400
Beautiful souls will always
be drawn to each other.

802
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:46,440
They'll keep getting closer.

803
00:35:46,800 --> 00:35:47,800
Just like...

804
00:35:48,239 --> 00:35:50,400
You're from Yuanmou, Yunnan,

805
00:35:51,719 --> 00:35:53,639
and I'm from Zhoukoudian, Beijing.

806
00:35:54,039 --> 00:35:57,238
Can I call you my friend?

807
00:35:57,239 --> 00:35:58,239
No.

808
00:35:58,320 --> 00:35:59,920
My best friend.

